{"tid":789630,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雲露娜自爆與奇洛李維斯「唔覺意」結咗婚","createTime":"2018-08-22T11:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T12:22:36.000Z","uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62e838e9136837293f31c41b07a3e0578758d7c8","tid":789630,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"荷李活經典銀幕情侶奇洛李維斯(Keanu Reeves)與雲露娜維達(Winona Ryder)第四度合作愛情喜劇《婚禮進行識》(Destination Wedding)。二人為宣傳新片，近日馬不停蹄接受外媒訪問，期間雲露娜竟自爆原來26年前同奇洛結咗婚！<br />\n<br />\n奇洛與雲露娜於1992年主演的《吸血殭屍：驚情四百年》(Bram Stoker&rsquo;s Dracula)堪稱年代經典，當時二人正值青春年華，外型皆屬男女神等級，尤其剛滿20歲的雲露娜的艷光四射，絕色容貌迷倒老中青三代，論樣貌身材在荷李活無出其右。<br />\n<br />\n雲露娜與奇洛日前為宣傳《婚禮進行識》受訪時，提到當年二人的合作，並大爆《驚情四百年》婚禮場面的驚人內幕：「事實上我們在電影裏結婚了。不，我發誓，我認為我們在現實生活中已經結婚了。因為Francis(導演哥普拉)用了真正的羅馬尼亞牧師，我們完成了整個婚禮儀式。所以，我想我們是真的結婚了。」<br />\n<br />\n對此事沒甚印象的奇洛則追問：「我們有說我願意？」搞到雲露娜沒好氣地說：「你不記得嗎？那天是情人節。」讓奇洛驚訝笑說：「天啊！我們真的結婚了。」當然，現實中雲露娜與奇洛的感情生活都各有各精彩。喜歡這對銀幕情侶的影迷大可以期待10月11日上映的《婚禮進行識》看兩人「再續前緣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OUgxmY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OUgxmY&d=T7HcUV2tDwmn75o%2F4oRumdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3da4ad56\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OUgxmY</a>"},{"pid":"58f11eff82bbd3ee6245adc55b8011d21cb36885","tid":789630,"uid":146720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"睇錯露雲娜"},{"pid":"bfbee6199d2ae5ba3a942f6d5a690ddc849f090b","tid":789630,"uid":20619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58f11eff82bbd3ee6245adc55b8011d21cb36885","tid":789630,"uid":146720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"睇錯露雲娜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:27:51.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f01dbae2968d550ca1632e677c2d412cd9f88fd","tid":789630,"uid":68375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"佢後生真係靚到仙女一樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nylon-img.imgix.net/featured_images/attachments/000/010/229/original/winona-ryder-reality-bites-main.jpg?auto=format&amp;ch=Width%2CDPR&amp;q=75&amp;w=640&amp;cs=strip&amp;crop=&amp;ixlib=js-1.2.0&amp;s=a4faaef234b54f3cb6c3076af24f50b0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnylon-img.imgix.net%2Ffeatured_images%2Fattachments%2F000%2F010%2F229%2Foriginal%2Fwinona-ryder-reality-bites-main.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26ch%3DWidth%252CDPR%26q%3D75%26w%3D640%26cs%3Dstrip%26crop%3D%26ixlib%3Djs-1.2.0%26s%3Da4faaef234b54f3cb6c3076af24f50b0&h=e40c6caa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92e9cadd5be4aaef36c0b29316a25dc6b6074dbc","tid":789630,"uid":12827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"現實中雲露娜與奇洛的感情生活都各有各精彩<br />\n<br />\n《奇洛李維斯死女友後好似毒到而家，咁都叫精彩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}